{"prompt": "Design a website for a health and wellness coaching business. The aesthetic should be refreshing, using a jonquil yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Thrive Wellness Coaching</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #f9e369; /* Jonquil Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #fdf8d7; /* A lighter, softer yellow */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --heading-color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #2c3e50 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/f9e369/2c3e50?text=Thrive+Wellness') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #services h2, #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .about-content, .contact-form {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item img {\n            width: 100px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .about-content p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--heading-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--heading-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Thrive Wellness Coaching</h1>\n  